E2FHAU.translated: ~z~我能赢纯粹是因为我比你强。你得多练练。

E2FHAU.original: ~z~Hey Luis, it's me.
E2FH_BDA
~z~Me and the freak want to see you, can you hang out?
E2FHAU.translated: ~z~我和疯子想见见你，你能来吗？

E2FHAU.original: E2FH_AXA
~z~Cool, cause it's good to know people don't give a shit about you, man.
E2FHAU.translated: ~z~好，认清一个人的丑恶嘴脸我血赚不亏，哥们。

E2FHAU.original: ~z~Well, when you got more time, hit one of us up.
E2FHAU.translated: ~z~好吧，哪天有空记得找我们，哪个都行。

E2FHAU.original: ~z~Cool bro, I'm down. I'll come and get you. I'll be there within two hours.
E2FHAU.translated: ~z~好啊兄弟，我来。我这就来接你们，大概两小时内到。

E2FHAU.original: E2FH_APA
~z~You boys up to anything? Want to hang out?
E2FHAU.translated: ~z~你们伙计俩忙吗？想不想出来玩？

E2FHAU.original: ~z~Oye, sorry H, but I got mad shit going on right now.
E2FHAU.translated: ~z~不好意思，H，我现在一堆破事忙炸了。

E2FHAU.original: ~z~Shit, sorry L, kind of tied up right now. Maybe later.
E2FHAU.translated: ~z~操，对不起，L。现在有点忙，晚点再说吧。

E2FHAU.original: E2FH_BUA
~z~Rique, it's Luis, bro. I was thinking I could really use a Bullet. You know of one that might be available?
E2FHAU.translated: ~z~Rique，我是Luis，兄弟。我现在正好需要辆Bullet。你有没有盯上哪辆能开的？

E2FHAU.original: ~z~Conõ, Rique, you the man. Thank you.
E2FH_ABA
E2FH_AWA
~z~I guess we'll finish when you're not on your period.
E2FHAU.translated: ~z~那就等你经期过了再补上这局吧。

E2FHAU.original: E2FH_AUA
~z~Great. I need someone to deal with Armando. That fool has been annoying the hell outta me. See you soon.
E2FHAU.translated: ~z~好的。正好能帮我治治Armando。我快被那傻逼烦死了。待会儿见。

E2FHAU.original: E2FH_AA
E2FH_BKA
~z~Damn, Luis. You one finessful motherfucker.
~z~Hey, we could play airhockey, at memory lanes?
E2FHAU.translated: ~z~嘿，可以去打保龄球馆打桌上冰球吗？

E2FHAU.original: ~z~I can't believe you won. I never lost to a woman before.
E2FHAU.translated: ~z~没想到你赢了。我从来没输给娘们过。

E2FHAU.original: ~z~I'm on my way, fool.
~z~I can't do that right now. Armando got me looking after some stuff for him. I don't want him to get angry again.
E2FHAU.translated: ~z~我现在来不了。Armando叫我帮他看批货。我不想又惹他生气。

E2FHAU.original: ~z~Here he is. I appreciate this, bro.
~z~Hey man, it's Henrique.
~z~Damn. I don't get to finish nothing these days.
E2FHAU.translated: ~z~妈的，最近我就没做完一件事过。
